## Overview

A native mobile application targeting iOS and Android.
The app will mirror the core functionality of the website and add offline support.

## Platform Targets

| Platform | Min Version | Priority |
|----------|-------------|----------|
| iOS | 16 | High |
| Android | 10 | High |

## Open Questions

- Which framework to use (React Native vs native)
- Whether to share a backend with the web or run a separate API
- Release timeline and beta testing strategy

## Planning Checklist

- [ ] Finalize framework decision
- [ ] Set up repo and CI
- [ ] Define API contract with backend
- [ ] Produce initial wireframes
